{"tid":2158432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[白痴始終佔多數]睇見格離post就作嘔，所以抵你班垃圾比港共用健康碼監控","createTime":"2020-08-15T17:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T17:44:33.000Z","uid":30274,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f8abff4d526d01f2d4a3d560235531d5a76c8e99","tid":2158432,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2157980\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2157980</a><br />\n一隻廢毒，明明係可以靠自己好，係要人用藥，身體冇事都搞到有事<br />\n你最多可以屌既然唔用藥，就唔應該留醫院而去隔離中心，free個床位出黎比有需要/重症患者用。咁呢個就係醫院嘅判斷失誤，繼續留一個後生，冇癥狀，低風險嘅確診者喺醫院<br />\n連唔想用藥搞到自己身體有不良反應都係錯? 咁抵你地遲早被新疆式管治。權威大哂吖嘛，可信吖嘛，一定冇錯架喎。佢話你應該食藥就應該食，你應該切左個腎就切左佢，應該點就點<br />\n你地on9你地要比支那用疫情控制唔緊要呀，話知你死，問題係你地班白痴嘅行為嘅後果導致我呢group人都一齊受呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"6fafb99f7948ac6a82554a1ea7fc08dadc44fb18","tid":2158432,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T17:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5830d14aad8e65359ea9829aaf45e2f16ce7471","tid":2158432,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T17:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71a7f0c45ef87929e08a43bffe822b4ca672232","tid":2158432,"uid":30274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T17:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}